narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned the grammar of Jewish Babylonian Aramaic, the reasons for various linguistic changes in the history of this dialect, and how it compares to other dialects of ancient Aramaic.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The main strength of this course is the focus upon modern linguistics in order to explain various phenomena exhibited in Babylonian Aramaic.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would highly recommend this course both because of the usefulness of learning Babylonian Aramaic and in the general linguistic knowledge gained.
